data.title: Biography
data.meta_description: Ari Up. Soundtrack: Here to Be Heard: The Story of the Slits. Ari Up was born on 17 January 1962 in Munich, West Germany [now Germany]. She was an actress, known for Here to Be Heard: The Story of the Slits (2017), Flickan, mamman och demonerna (2016) and Joe Strummer: The Future Is Unwritten (2007). She died on 20 October 2010 in Los Angeles, California, USA.
data.text: Ari Up was born on January 17, 1962 in Munich, West Germany [now Germany]. She was an actress, known for Here to Be Heard: The Story of the Slits (2017), Flickan, mamman och demonerna (2016) and Joe Strummer: The Future Is Unwritten (2007). She died on October 20, 2010 in Los Angeles, California, USA.
